 then chucked it aside,and that aggression still not quenched,she shot her right arm up,and to the left,now that spike cutting a clean mark through the trunk of the tree the root had come from.It wasn't seconds later that,that tree then fell freely and landing with a loud crach and thud.<br>
She stood there,looking at the fallen tree then,her fists clentched in tight fists,her chest heaving as her breathing hardened,not from the energy she used,but from the heat of the sun that had been taking its toll on her.<br>
The sun not only making her agressive,but disturbing her eyes,which were sensitive to light,but luckily she had a second lid that closed around her eyes,making her eyes darker than usual,but shaded them well enough.<br>
<br>
Relaxing for the moment,she unballed her fists,that right spike soon disappearing back into her flesh as she relaxed her muscles.Turning now,she made her way once again toward the village.Once reaching the top of a hill which over looked the village,she stopped for the moment,bringing her left hand up,and wripping the beads of sweat from her forehead.Then letting her hand drop back down to her side.She stood there for a long moment,just staring at the village,she was an amazon here,but she still couldnt help but feel unwelcomed.It didnt really matter,she had gotten this far,and need to get out of the heat.<br>
Ah,but the heat had already taken it's toll,she was exhausted.She tethered a little,then colapsed,falling to her back.A slight groan escaping her throat as she lay there.She felt weak and unable to mobilize,all she could do was bring her right hand up to cover her face from the rays of the sun....<br>
Maybe she'd just lay here until the sun-sets..... <p>---Everybody Got a sanity------I've got a split personality---</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A> at: 8/3/01 4:20:09 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(8/4/01 3:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=262.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ....Damn the heat!....</span><hr size=1> She didn't know how long she had been lying there,in the open,the sun blaring down on her.She must have passed out.Her chest was still heaving,as she pulled her hand away from her face.She gained some energy back,and with that little bit of energy,she braced her elbows onto the ground,and pushed herself up into a sitting position.She then settled the palms of her hands on the ground,and pushed her self up,and onto her feet,however now crouching.<br>
<br>
She then brought her right hand up and shaded her eyes as she looked down upon the village.&quot;Get going.&quot; She told herself.She then stood up,and straightened herself out.It was too damn hot,and again her hands were clentched into tight fists,the veins in her arms pulsing with every nerve in her body trying to fight the itch to go down and destroy something.,even if it would drain her energy...all she felt was like killing and destroying.&quot;Maybe coming to Themiscrya was a bad idea....?&quot;Again,she talked to herself.<br>
&quot;Ha,I kept telling you to stay in the cave....moron.&quot;Those words were spat from her mouth,unable to control her 'dark side' from popping up from time to time.It came to often that she was heared humiliating herself or making stupid comments,something that always got her on the edge,she couldnt keep that voice out of her head,and it drove her crazy.Crazy enough that she let out a scream of frustration and anger.&quot;Go Away!&quot;<br>
&quot;You're stuck with me!Besides....i'm your only friend.Now move it before you get us killed.&quot;That stupid voice.She brought her hands up and held her head in her hands,eyes closed tightly,teeth clentched.Her breathing becoming more heavy.&quot;Go away.&quot;She spoke once again,quietly through clentched teeth.<br>
<br>
A few moments later,and all quite.The veins in her arms,and any other visable part of her body were visably pulsing,her demon form threatening to show itself.And it began.The flesh on her forarms slowly began to tear,though she tried to fight it,but with little energy she was failing.The tips of spikes began to slowly peek from the torn flesh.Even the back of her shirt began to rip open as these spikes slowly tore through the flesh and the clothing she wore.A growl now escaped her throat,though she had been in demon form once or twice before,she was yet to be use to the pain of her flesh tearing each time this happened.<br>
<br>
She fell to her knees,her hands digging into the soil beneath her hands.She was fighting it alright.The spikes stopped growing only reaching half thier size of 10-15 inches.<br>
Though the spikes had now ceased,they were still visable.Her entire back almost completly covered with 5-8 inch spikes.A 12 inch spike coming from each of her wrists,and running the length of her arms,while smaller spikes petruded on different areas of the arms.All other areas of her body,fortunate enough not to be covered in spikes at that moment.She was going to control this,or die of exhaustion while trying.....<br>
<br>
And she stayed there,on her knees,still her hands dug into the dirt.Eye still tightly closed.Using every mental ability she had to fight this urge.... <p>---Everybody Got a sanity------I've got a split personality---</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 132<br> <font color=#993300>(8/7/01 3:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=262.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Consort</span><hr size=1> ::A deep, curling mist passes over the hill and then settles over Zelia enveloping her as she kneels on the floor. It blocks out the sun yet the light seeps through so that things can be seen. Then in a thunderous flash the god Poseidon appears before Zelia as she is having her inner conflict. Poseidon is wearing a small, thin, see-through loin cloth made of white velvet. And on his feet he has a pair of golden sandles. The god folds his arms across his muscular chest and looks down upon the woman. His curls fall across his face and his blue eyes glow with intrigue.::<br>
