<br>
Slowly she stood,her head twitching slighty her hands clentching the soil she had torn from the ground,all instinct she had was telling her to attack the god,but instead a smirk crosses those crimson lips,as she controled that part of herself.<br>
<br>
&quot;As a matter of fact....i'm feeling much better.&quot;As she spoke,she relaxed her hands,the dirt freely falling from her hands,though she acctually was feeling a little better,it didnt look it,her eyes were still darkened from the second lid,and those spikes still petruded from her body...<br>
<br>
