<br>
She then felt his pressence fading,what a relief.<br>
<br>
But then,Hypnos had to go and do the eye thing,and her eyes diolated.She brought the back of her right hand up and blocked out the lights,what was he trying to do,blind her?She closed her eyes tightly,and fell to one knee,her left hand braced against the ground,a low growl escaping those crimson lips.She was getting a major headache,and surprisingly her alter ego had yet to take over,another relief.<br>
<br>
Well,this certainly has been quite a trip,next time,she'll take her own advise and stay in her happy little cave.<br>
<br>
Oh wait,lets try to make things interesting,shall we....<br>
<br>
And without further ado,she let out another growl,this one louder,and more threatening,and her hands balled up into tight fists,she stood up,and as she did so a spike of 12 inches in length,beginning from the wrists of each arm tears through her skin and running the length of her arms.And suddenly with great speed,she runs toward the large oak where Hypnos was,her left arm coming up across her chest,then jolted out and across the stem of the tree,slicing it clean in half and causing the large tree to thump to the ground.She then jerked her body back the other direction,and bringing both her arms up,fists inward,spikes out and crossed,she sets the very tip of the razor sharp spike directly at the throat of Hypnos,with a simple movement she could bring her arms down and embed the spike into the throat of the god.Not that it could do much damage,but her alter ego took surface and she was pissed.<br>
<br>
&quot;Whats with the light show?&quot;She spoke angrily.<br>
<br>
Sure,Hypnos seemed to have been trying to do a nice thing,but to this side of her,it didnt matter.<br>
